    <item>
      <title>印度储备银行行长达斯表示，通胀必须降至 4% 才能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/rbi-governor-das-says-inflation-must-slow-to-4-for-a-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度储备银行行长沙克提坎塔·达斯表示，印度的通胀率必须显示出可持续地稳定在央行 4% 目标附近的迹象，然后才会考虑降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/rbi-governor-das-says-inflation-must-slow-to-4-for-a-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 13:56:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯哄抬价格计划将产生什么效果？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-20/what-would-the-harris-price-gouging-plan-do-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的经济顾问迈克·派尔谈到了她提出的打击哄抬物价的计划。派尔表示，该计划将重点关注食品和杂货行业、紧急情况以及现有州法律。他正在接受“彭博监视”节目的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-20/what-would-the-harris-price-gouging-plan-do-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 13:52:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西雷亚尔走弱，因央行行长对加息表示怀疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/brazil-real-weakens-as-central-banker-casts-doubt-on-rate-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西央行行长罗伯托·坎波斯·内托表示，虽然正在考虑加息，但由于国际前景改善且预期未来几个月通胀将会放缓，加息的可能性低于市场目前的预测，随后，巴西雷亚尔走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/brazil-real-weakens-as-central-banker-casts-doubt-on-rate-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 13:42:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国强劲的工资增长加剧了欧洲央行的通胀困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/germany-s-strong-wage-growth-adds-to-ecb-s-inflation-struggle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国央行表示，德国强劲的工资增长势头并未减弱，并可能使通胀维持高位——这对正在努力将价格涨幅恢复至 2% 目标的欧洲央行来说是一个令人担忧的信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/germany-s-strong-wage-growth-adds-to-ecb-s-inflation-struggle</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国电动汽车调查的推进，欧盟计划对特斯拉汽车征收 9% 的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/eu-plans-9-tariff-on-tesla-cars-as-china-ev-probe-advances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟周二表示，计划对从中国进口的特斯拉汽车征收额外 9% 的关税，同时欧盟已向汽车制造商通报了其决定草案，将对从中国进口的电动汽车征收最终关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/eu-plans-9-tariff-on-tesla-cars-as-china-ev-probe-advances</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥与斯洛文尼亚携手计划推出低收益武士销售计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/mexico-markets-samurai-bonds-as-yields-stay-low-despite-boj-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥计划近两年来首次通过武士债券筹集资金，与斯洛文尼亚一道考虑利用日本债券收益率仍然相对较低的优势发行债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/mexico-markets-samurai-bonds-as-yields-stay-low-despite-boj-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 02:12:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
